{"tid":2064163,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國商會游說政府「別放棄14億人市場」 主席為匯控高層","createTime":"2020-06-14T15:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-14T22:37:41.000Z","uid":39464,"like":15,"dislike":411,"uniUserReply":86,"replies":[{"pid":"264418d8dbfd3e1bf6e0ae7cc4acd6115867c21f","tid":2064163,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:08:32.000Z","msg":"英國《泰晤士報》報道，一個親中的英國組織正在游說富時100指數的公司，希望這批藍籌公司向英國政府陳述與中國關係惡化的風險。<br />\n<br />\n據報道引述英中貿易協會（CBBC）的文件指出，「脫歐後首要的策略，不應該是放棄一個擁有14億人的國家和市場。」<br />\n<br />\n英中貿易協會的主席為匯控（0005）的公共事務主管Sherard Cowper-Coles，而董事會成員包括渣打集團（2888）、英國石油及葛蘭素史克的高層。報道指他們正積極接觸在中國有業務的英國大型上市企業去支持這個游說運動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1592143958206&amp;issue=20200614\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mpfinance.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1592143958206%26issue%3D20200614&d=B%2FbWfq3Pg5BEfhRE9gwZ8v7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=fec45eee\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.mpfinance.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1592143958206&amp;issue=20200614</a>"},{"pid":"1e146c51cb80fec2125b27aec0a5c91520259a29","tid":2064163,"uid":53524,"like":89,"dislike":0,"score":89,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:09:46.000Z","msg":"轉行賣鴉片咪得"},{"pid":"851985d017220e45b88e6ab5bb722f07488e5651","tid":2064163,"uid":132587,"like":152,"dislike":2,"score":150,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:11:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/e5f033b3-b369-4b66-8b40-2a37665f1fa1/640.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmegapx-assets.dcard.tw%2Fimages%2Fe5f033b3-b369-4b66-8b40-2a37665f1fa1%2F640.jpeg&h=fdd0a369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港人養大你<br />\n少少情誼都唔念<br />\n唔該搬上大陸<br />\n無香港人會可憐你地"},{"pid":"879c67929f638004cdb4725c74e715b258459de2","tid":2064163,"uid":335434,"like":116,"dislike":0,"score":116,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-14T15:11:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-bb75b3f872592bdc06e2593f465215fd_1440w.jpg\" data